{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213055, "create_time": 1655119591, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "如果是在说唐山明显对不上啊", "timestamp": 1655119591}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213059, "create_time": 1655119657, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 不是唐山的事，是构造一个单独的案例", "timestamp": 1655119657}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213072, "create_time": 1655119827, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "什么叫动手动脚", "timestamp": 1655119827}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213082, "create_time": 1655119956, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 比如扇了一巴掌", "timestamp": 1655119956}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213123, "create_time": 1655120571, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "都不犯罪，触犯刑法是一件比较困难的事情", "timestamp": 1655120571}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213136, "create_time": 1655120807, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "必须要说明性别，最终是否构成犯罪还是取决于甲和乙的性别", "timestamp": 1655120807}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213138, "create_time": 1655120881, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 其实我想问的是，当双方逐步升级的过程中，什么情况下算是在防卫？什么情况下也算是在犯罪？", "timestamp": 1655120881}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213140, "create_time": 1655120913, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "如果甲和乙性别相同，那么乙承担主要责任；\n如果甲和乙性别不同，那么男方承担几乎全部责任。", "timestamp": 1655120913}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213142, "create_time": 1655120976, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 比如我打了你一巴掌，于是你拿玻璃瓶敲我的头，于是我拿刀捅了你一刀，于是你对我开了一枪", "timestamp": 1655120976}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213154, "create_time": 1655121199, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "甲和乙说话，乙和甲说话。甲对乙动手动脚。乙对甲动手动脚。事件到此结束。甲的行为是否构成犯罪？乙的行为是否构成犯罪？", "timestamp": 1655121199}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213155, "create_time": 1655121220, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "学习洞主来个简写", "timestamp": 1655121220}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213174, "create_time": 1655121504, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "如果甲对乙有明显的人身财产侵害意图，乙的行为应该属于正当防卫。而且我始终认为法律应该考虑到甲是否远比乙强壮或者对乙能否确实构成威胁。比如乙是小孩，或者甲拿着刀（指构成威胁），如果甲明显对乙构成威胁，则乙更是正当防卫。", "timestamp": 1655121504}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213187, "create_time": 1655121702, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 假设甲和乙强壮相同", "timestamp": 1655121702}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213193, "create_time": 1655121764, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 所以说是否属于正当防卫，要看是否明显构成威胁？", "timestamp": 1655121764}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213207, "create_time": 1655121929, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Francis: 假如例子改成，甲先动手扇了乙一巴掌，然后乙拿起玻璃瓶开始连续敲击甲的头部，此时甲拿起身边的刀捅向乙，事件到此结束。那这时候甲是否算是在面临人身安全威胁情况下的正当防卫吗？", "timestamp": 1655121929}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 213433, "create_time": 1655125126, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "不用说那么多细节，都是国男的错", "timestamp": 1655125126}], "create_time": 1655119481, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1655125126, "likenum": 8, "n_attentions": 8, "n_comments": 16, "pid": 64544, "poll": null, "reply": 16, "text": "甲欲加乙的联系方式，被乙拒绝。甲不满，对乙动手动脚。乙拿起玻璃瓶敲击甲的头部。事件到此结束。甲的行为是否构成犯罪？乙的行为是否构成犯罪？", "timestamp": 1655119481}}